## 🔖 Plugin Metadata

**pyproject.toml 設定**：
```toml
[tool.mcp.plugin]
name = "goldenegg"
version = "0.1.0"
description = "提供持股查詢與儲存的 MCP 插件"
entrypoint = "mcp_plugin.goldenegg_plugin"
tools = ["save_holdings", "get_holdings"]
resources = ["broker_configs", "ocr_history", "holdings_schema"]
prompts = ["save_ocr_data", "query_holdings", "broker_integration"]

[tool.poetry.dependencies]
python = "^3.10"
fastmcp = "^0.1.0"
pydantic = "^2.0"
httpx = "^0.27.0"
```
├── mcp_plugin/
│   └── goldenegg_plugin.py  # FastMCP server 主程式（main.py）
├── pyproject.toml      # metadata 設定
└── start.sh            # 啟動腳本